{"word":"H7878 - שִׂיחַ - sîyach - see'-akh - Commune","slug":"H7878","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שִׂיחַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sîyach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>see'-akh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Commune"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05D9;&#x05D7; - s&#x0301;&#x0131;&#x0302;yach</b> - <i>see'-akh</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>ponder</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>converse</i> (with oneself, and hence aloud) or (transitively) <i>utter: - </i>commune, complain, declare, meditate, muse, pray, speak, talk (with)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7808\">H7808</a>, <a href=\"#/H7879\">H7879</a>, <a href=\"#/H7881\">H7881</a>"}]}